(ns server.main-create-server
  (:require [commander]
            [util]
            [ajax.core :refer [GET POST]]
            ;[xhr2]
            [cljs.core.async :refer [chan put! take! >! <! buffer dropping-buffer sliding-buffer timeout close! alts!]]
            [cljs.core.async :refer-macros [go go-loop alt!]]
          ;  [cljs-http :as client]
            [cljs-http.client :as http]
            [clojure.string :as str]))

(enable-console-print!)
;(set! js/XMLHttpRequest xhr2)

(def app-state (atom {}))

(defn dump-object [obj]
  (println (.inspect util obj)))

(defn command-handler []
  (let [cli (doto commander
              (.version "0.1.0")
              (.arguments "<name>")
              (.action (fn [name]
                   (swap! app-state assoc :arg name)))
              (.option  "-p , --project-id <id>" "Provide a project id")
              (.parse  (.-argv js/process)))]
    (if (= (.-args.length cli ) 0)
      (.help cli #(clojure.string/replace % #"main-create-server" "create-server")))))

(defn main! []
  (let [cli (command-handler)]
    (println @app-state)
  ))



(defprotocol IServer
  (create-server [this])
  (destroy-server [this])
  (start-server [this])
  (stop-server [this]))


(defrecord PacketServer [name project-id]
  IServer
  (create-server [this] (println name))
  (destroy-server  [this] (println name))
  (start-server  [this] (println name))
  (stop-server  [this] (println name))
  )

(defn http-get [uri]
  (let [request (http/get uri {:headers {"X-Auth-Token" auth}})]
    (go
      (let [resp (<! request)
            body (:body resp)]
        body))))
